command-line utility, &quot;flyctl&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;That said, that&#39;s not how I want us to define a dev shell.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our current solution has issues. I don&#39;t like that it has &lt;code&gt;import &amp;lt;nixpkgs&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;.
